{"id":"lyr_546L6I-y_MTExNg_0017","text":"我最初抓緊他的雙手 從來不愛自由","structure":{"line_index":17,"char_count":15},"semantics":{"themes":["依賴","不愛自由","佔有"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["最初","抓緊","雙手","不愛","自由"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,4,3,3,9,3,3,3,9,0,0,3,4,2,0],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["ngo5","zeoi3","co1","zaa1","gan2","taa1","dik1","soeng1","sau2","cung4","loi4","bat1","oi3","zi6","jau4"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"最初","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"抓緊","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"他","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"的","pos":"PART"},{"text":"雙手","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"從來不","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"愛","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"自由","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"再次回溯到最初，強調當時對對方的依賴，甚至不追求自由，只想被擁有。"},"source":{"title":"多得他","artists":["王菲"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1116","prev_line_id":"lyr_546L6I-y_MTExNg_0016","next_line_id":"lyr_546L6I-y_MTExNg_0018","paragraph_id":"para_05"}}
{"id":"lyr_546L6I-y_MTExNg_0018","text":"能讓我永遠地擁有 已覺真的富有","structure":{"line_index":18,"char_count":14},"semantics":{"themes":["滿足","依賴","擁有"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["永遠","擁有","富有"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,2,5,5,5,2,9,5,5,4,3,3,4,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["nang4","joeng6","ngo5","wing5","jyun5","dei6","jung2","jau5","ji5","gok3","zan1","dik1","fu3","jau5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"能","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"讓","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"永遠","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"地","pos":"PART"},{"text":"擁有","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"已覺","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"真的","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"富有","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"表達了當時認為只要能永遠擁有對方，就感到非常滿足和富有。"},"source":{"title":"多得他","artists":["王菲"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1116","prev_line_id":"lyr_546L6I-y_MTExNg_0017","next_line_id":"lyr_546L6I-y_MTExNg_0019","paragraph_id":"para_05"}}
{"id":"lyr_546L6I-y_MTExNg_0019","text":"那料這又抹掉眼淚也要靠我的手","structure":{"line_index":19,"char_count":14},"semantics":{"themes":["獨立","自立","成長"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["料到","抹掉","眼淚","靠","手"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,2,5,2,4,2,5,2,5,4,4,5,3,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["naa5","liu6","ze5","jau6","mut3","diu6","ngaan5","leoi6","jaa5","jiu3","kaau3","ngo5","dik1","sau2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"那料","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"這","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"又","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"抹掉","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"眼淚","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"也","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"要","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"靠","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"的","pos":"PART"},{"text":"手","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"再次轉折，表達了如今即使面對悲傷，也學會依靠自己的力量去克服。"},"source":{"title":"多得他","artists":["王菲"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1116","prev_line_id":"lyr_546L6I-y_MTExNg_0018","next_line_id":"lyr_546L6I-y_MTExNg_0020","paragraph_id":"para_05"}}
{"id":"lyr_546L6I-y_MTExNg_0020","text":"即使他已愛我多久 仍會高飛遠走","structure":{"line_index":20,"char_count":14},"semantics":{"themes":["分離","自由","必然"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["即使","愛","多久","高飛遠走"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[3,9,3,5,4,5,3,9,0,3,3,5,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["zik1","si2","taa1","ji5","oi3","ngo5","do1","gau2","jing4","gou1","fei1","jyun5","zau2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"即使","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"他","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"已","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"愛","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"多久","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"仍會","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"高飛遠走","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"指出即使對方曾經愛過，最終還是會離開，強調了關係的無常。"},"source":{"title":"多得他","artists":["王菲"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1116","prev_line_id":"lyr_546L6I-y_MTExNg_0019","next_line_id":"lyr_546L6I-y_MTExNg_0021","paragraph_id":"para_05"}}
{"id":"lyr_546L6I-y_MTExNg_0021","text":"他的愛意反覆改變我 也許相戀得太多","structure":{"line_index":21,"char_count":16},"semantics":{"themes":["改變","關係","經驗"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["愛意","反覆","改變","相戀","太多"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[3,3,4,4,9,3,9,4,5,5,9,9,3,4,3],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["taa1","dik1","oi3","ji3","faan2","fuk1","goi2","bin3","ngo5","jaa5","heoi2","lyun2","dak1","taai3","do1"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"他","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"的","pos":"PART"},{"text":"愛意","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"反覆","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"改變","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"也許","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"相戀","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"得太多","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"反思這段關係對自己的改變，認為相戀的經驗太多，導致了現在的狀態。"},"source":{"title":"多得他","artists":["王菲"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1116","prev_line_id":"lyr_546L6I-y_MTExNg_0020","next_line_id":"lyr_546L6I-y_MTExNg_0022","paragraph_id":"para_06"}}
{"id":"lyr_546L6I-y_MTExNg_0022","text":"人亦漸漸不知對錯","structure":{"line_index":22,"char_count":8},"semantics":{"themes":["迷惘","失去方向","成長"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["人","漸漸","不知","對錯"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,2,2,2,3,3,4,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["jan4","jik6","zim6","zim6","bat1","zi1","deoi3","co3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"人","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"亦","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"漸漸","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"不知","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"對錯","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"描述了因為關係的複雜和變遷，導致自己漸漸失去判斷對錯的能力。"},"source":{"title":"多得他","artists":["王菲"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1116","prev_line_id":"lyr_546L6I-y_MTExNg_0021","next_line_id":"lyr_546L6I-y_MTExNg_0023","paragraph_id":"para_06"}}
{"id":"lyr_546L6I-y_MTExNg_0023","text":"天生孤單過路再上路也不清楚","structure":{"line_index":23,"char_count":13},"semantics":{"themes":["孤單","迷惘","重新開始"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["天生","孤單","過路","上路","清楚"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[3,3,3,3,4,2,4,2,5,3,3,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["tin1","sang1","gu1","daan1","gwo3","lou6","zoi3","lou6","jaa5","bat1","cing1","co2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"天生","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"孤單","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"過路","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"再","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"上路","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"也","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"不","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"清楚","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"將孤單的狀態追溯到天生，並描述了重新上路時的迷惘和不確定。"},"source":{"title":"多得他","artists":["王菲"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1116","prev_line_id":"lyr_546L6I-y_MTExNg_0022","next_line_id":"lyr_546L6I-y_MTExNg_0024","paragraph_id":"para_06"}}
{"id":"lyr_546L6I-y_MTExNg_0024","text":"要看得清楚卻不必需要那點戀火","structure":{"line_index":24,"char_count":14},"semantics":{"themes":["獨立","看清","放下"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["清楚","不必","需要","戀火"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[4,4,3,3,9,4,3,3,3,4,5,9,9,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["jiu3","hon3","dak1","cing1","co2","koek3","bat1","bit1","seoi1","jiu3","naa5","dim2","lyun2","fo2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"要","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"看","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"得","pos":"PART"},{"text":"清楚","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"卻","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"不必","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"需要","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"那點","pos":"DET"},{"text":"戀火","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"表達了即使需要看清，但已經不再需要那份戀愛的情感，象徵著放下。"},"source":{"title":"多得他","artists":["王菲"],"lyricists":["林夕"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1116","prev_line_id":"lyr_546L6I-y_MTExNg_0023","next_line_id":"lyr_546L6I-y_MTExNg_0025","paragraph_id":"para_06"}}
